title: Cable & Deadpool
description:
Cable & Deadpool features Cable, the time-traveling son of Cyclops and Madelyne Pryor and everybody's favourite merc with a mouth, Deadpool. Published by Marvel the series was a mixture of humor, action, and intricate plot lines and lasted 50 issues before being canceled to make way for new individual series for each title character.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
